# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and on checkout. The Rust crates
# embed ~30 files via include_str!/include_bytes! (rules TOML, snapshots,
# bundles); CRLF checkouts on Windows would change those bytes and break
# hashes/goldens, so eol=lf is mandatory rather than core.autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalized or diffed as text.
*.png binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.wasm binary
*.gz binary
